claim.claim-text:
1. A microwave susceptor comprising: 
a dimensionally stable substrate; 
a plastic film laminated to the substrate; and 
a generally continuous layer of metal deposited on the plastic film, wherein 
the metal layer comprises a generally contiguous microwave interactive area; 
the metal layer contains a plurality of microwave transparent areas that enhance the heating of the metal layer; 
the transparent areas are spaced apart from each other; 
the transparent areas are distributed across an entire surface area defining the microwave susceptor; and 
each of the transparent areas has a major dimension of about one eighth the length of a wavelength of microwaves generated by an operating microwave oven.
